@Node Main "Galaxy Documentation"

@{b}Galaxy Release 1.0@{ub}

The idea for the "Galaxy"-Blanker comes from the BTD-Blanker "Galaxy"
by Markus Illenser, who has taken it from a EGS-Blanker by Uli Sigmund,
but I'm using Garshneblanker, because BTD has too many bugs in
the actually version, so I've rewritten the Blanker for Garshne.

